descriptionHtml:
since there are no khajiit tattoos so far i decided to make one, this mod its just a retexture of tigersan & wolverinehowlett more muscular man mod so if you dont like muscular khajiits do not download this mod, there are still some issues im trying to fix like for example in the current version 1.0 depending on the lighting the tattoo fades into color gray im still trying to fix this, if anyone knows how to fix this then im all ears.
Anpther thing is that like all tattoo mods ive seen it affects all the npc with the same race lucky for khajiit users there arent many khajiits through the game showing their bodies.

Requirements:
None
author: buba1
